# Summary
The Amplitude Activation Braze streaming integration enables real-time forwarding of Amplitude events and user data to Braze, requiring Braze API Endpoint, API Key, and App ID for setup. It supports configurable user ID mapping, event filtering, and property selection for both event streaming and user profile updates.

